snippet.title: Epic Tabletop RPG Adventure Awaits! Clash of Clans New Season
snippet.description:
Step into a world of magic, mystery, and epic quests! Our latest season brings the thrill of tabletop RPGs to life. Whether you're a seasoned adventurer or a new hero, this is your chance to prove your mettle. With new challenges, exclusive rewards, and endless adventure, the path to glory starts here!

Learn more about what is to come: https://supercell.com/en/games/clashofclans/blog/news/tabletop-rpg-adventure-awaits/


Follow us on our Socials!
Twitter ► https://twitter.com/ClashofClans/
Instagram ► https://www.instagram.com/clashofclans 
Facebook ► https://www.facebook.com/ClashofClans 
TikTok ► https://www.tiktok.com/@clashofclans

Attack. Defend. Strategize. Download for free for mobile devices. supr.cl/PlayClashOfClans

From rage-­filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.
A network connection is also required.

FEATURES
- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

Chief, are you having problems? Visit https://help.supercellsupport.com/clash-of-clans/en/

Privacy Policy:
https://supercell.com/en/privacy-policy/

Terms of Service:
https://supercell.com/en/terms-of-service/

Parent’s Guide:
https://supercell.com/en/parents/

snippet.title: What is NASA Searching for in DEEP SEA
snippet.description:
Teeth aligners by toothsi close teeth gaps and straighten crooked teeth. Book your FREE teeth scan now - https://toothsi.makeo.app/3MpQeoF
Discount Code: GET24TS

What is NASA searching for in the deep ocean? Yes, what secrets lie 10 km beneath the ocean's surface that NASA is desperately trying to uncover?

Few people know that just off the coast of Florida, at a depth of 20 meters in the ocean, lies the world's only underwater lab called Aquarius Reef Base. Every year, NASA sends 5-6 researchers and astronauts—yes, astronauts—to this lab for several weeks as part of a special project called Project NEEMO (NASA’s Extreme Environment Mission Operations). These NASA scientists are referred to as "Aquanauts." But that's not all. NASA also has an autonomous underwater vehicle named ORPHEUS, which is diving 10 km deep into the ocean to conduct research. But why is a space agency like NASA working in the depths of the ocean? After all, the U.S. has a separate organization, NOAA (National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration), specifically for ocean research.
What is so urgent that a 2-month deadline has been set? Let's try to understand what's going on in the minds of NASA scientists and whether we should be concerned about it.

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS | Real Madrid 2-0 Real Betis | LaLiga 2024/25
snippet.description:
Real Madrid beat Betis at the Santiago Bernabéu stadium ahead of the international break. A great second half saw Ancelotti's side put the game beyond doubt. Mbappé stole the show, scoring his first brace for Real Madrid and coming off to a standing ovation when he was replaced by Modrić. His first goal came with a first-time finish following a stunning back-heel assist from Valverde, and his second came from the penalty spot after Vini Jr had been brought down.

snippet.title: Homemade Maharashtrian Sunday Brunch at Sharvari Wagh’s Dadar Home | Ep 140 | Curly Tales
snippet.description:
Be The First To Watch All Videos. Download the CurlyTales App:
https://curlytale.page.link/DwNd

In this episode of Sunday Brunch Presented By @Samsung Galaxy Book4 Series, we’re joined by the fabulous Sharvari Wagh! 

From winning Fresh Face to becoming India's National Crush, Sharvari has taken Bollywood by storm with her roles & her dazzling smile!
We visited her beautiful Dadar home overlooking the sea link and had a heartfelt chat about her memories of Dadar, her love for food, and her journey to Bollywood, including winning the Best Debut Award and her upcoming projects. 

But that’s not all! We also indulged in a delicious homemade Maharashtrian feast featuring 7-step Misal, Kothimbir Vadi, Piyush, Shakarpare, Besan Ladoo, and more—bringing the true essence of a Marathi Mulgi to life.

The fun continued with a quirky game where I used the Samsung Galaxy Book4 Pro 360's Multi Control Feature to drag emojis onto the screen. The twist? Sharvari had to deliver famous Bollywood dialogues based on the emojis—in Marathi! And we topped it off with a thrilling fan interaction call.

Sharvari’s love for Maharashtrian food proves she’s a typical Marathi Mulgi through and through. We had a blast at brunch, and we hope you enjoy watching it as much as we did filming it!

00:00 - Maharashtrian Spread at Sharvari's Dadar Home
02:02 - Sharvari's guide to Dadar
05:15 - Drag & Drop game to test Sharvari's marathi skills
08:47 - Delicious Maharashtrian Brunch

We visited her beautiful Dadar home overlooking the sea link and had a heartfelt chat about her memories of Dadar, her love for food, and her journey to Bollywood, including winning the Best Debut Award and her upcoming projects. 

But that’s not all! We also indulged in a delicious homemade Maharashtrian feast featuring 7-step Misal, Kothimbir Vadi, Piyush, Shakarpare, Besan Ladoo, and more—bringing the true essence of a Marathi Mulgi to life.

The fun continued with a quirky game where I used the Samsung Galaxy Book4 Pro 360's Multi Control Feature to drag emojis onto the screen. The twist? Sharvari had to deliver famous Bollywood dialogues based on the emojis—in Marathi! And we topped it off with a thrilling fan interaction call.

Sharvari’s love for Maharashtrian food proves she’s a typical Marathi Mulgi through and through. We had a blast at brunch, and we hope you enjoy watching it as much as we did filming it!

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Kaffara Episode 36 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 1st September - HAR PAL GEO

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. However, due to a conspiracy, objections arise about their closeness. Salar, once again, avoids the issue, leaving Sitara to face doubts from her own family.
Can Sitara prove she’s not guilty? Will Salar help her avoid further mistreatment? Will her family support Sitara? Can Salar show he genuinely cares? Will there be more plots against Sitara?

Gyaarah Gyaarah,
An anomaly connects 2 police officers across timelines through a walkie-talkie that comes alive at 11:11. As the two help each other solve cases, the reality around them changes forever.

Officer Yug tries solving a cold case with the support of senior cop Vamika. But in a twist of fate, a defunct walkie-talkie springs to life at 11:11 PM, connecting Yug to a past Officer Shaurya.

Cast:- Raghav Juyal, Kritika Kamra, Dhairya Karwa, Aakash Dixit, Mukti Mohan
Directed by:- Umesh Bist
Written by:- Puja Banerji, Sunjoy Shekhar, Sameer Saral Sharma, Gautam Govind Sharma

Episode 4178: Abdul Ka Udhaar
--------------------------------------------------------
Abdul opens up about his troubles to the members of the Gokuldham Society, who immediately offer to lend him money, but he graciously declines their help. How will Abdul manage to clear his debts on his own?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Honey Singh on 'Glory', Mafia Mundeer, Ghostwriting, International Villager 2 | Podcast | The Quint
snippet.description:
Become The Quint's member now: https://rb.gy/yj715w

In this episode of 'Do I Like It', Prateek Lidhoo talks to one of the most impactful artists of Indian hip hop, Yo Yo Honey Singh. He talks about his comeback as a producer, the writing process of his album 'Glory', and whether he has used ghostwriters in the past. Watch till the end to find out updates about his much anticipated album 'International Villager 2'. 

Chapters:
0:00 - Intro
1:13 - Why is the new album called 'Glory'?
2:50 - What about 'International Villager 2'?
4:27 - How did he find the sound of the album
8:13 - Did Honey Singh use ghostwriters on 'International Villager' and 'Desi Kalakaar'
16:11 - How does Honey Singh feel when people say that he uses ghostwriters?
20:48 - "Mafia Mundeer was never a team"
25:21 - Which was the hardest song to crack?
27:25 - Honey Singh's most underrated song
28:06 - Honey SIngh's least favourite superhit song
29:39 - 10 year plan and 'International Villager 2' update

Video: The Quint
Music: BMG

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 4177 | 30 Aug 2024 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 4177: Abdul Ki Dukaan
--------------------------------------------------------
The news that Abdul is attempting to sell his shop sends shockwaves through the colony, leaving all its members stunned and concerned. Will they find a solution for him?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - Ep 4177 | 30 Aug 2024
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #16yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. snippet.title: Noida Kings vs Meerut Mavericks | UPT20 Highlights | JioCinema & Sports18
snippet.description:
Noida Kings vs Meerut Mavericks | UPT20 Highlights | JioCinema & Sports18 

The Meerut Mavericks continue their unbeaten streak in the UPT20! In a challenging match, captain Rinku Singh delivered a standout performance with 64 off 35 balls, setting a formidable target of 164. Despite a strong start from Kavya Teotia, the Noida Super Kings, led by Nitish Rana, fell short with 152 runs. The Mavericks' resilience and Singh's crucial innings ensured their victory once again.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.
